---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Pagani North — Official Site">
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-image" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    <div class="hero-shade" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    <div class="hero-content reveal">
      <p class="eyebrow">Pagani North</p>
      <h1>PAGANI<br />NORTH</h1>
      <p class="hero-line">Intimate songs about memory, responsibility, longing, and the parts of ourselves we sometimes have to leave behind.</p>
      <div class="actions">
        <a class="button button-primary" href="https://distrokid.com/hyperfollow/paganinorth/the-ghost-of-the-boy" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Listen to the album</a>
        <a class="button button-ghost" href="#ghost">Enter the story</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <a class="scroll-cue" href="#latest" aria-label="Scroll to latest release"><span></span>Scroll</a>
  </section>

  <section id="latest" class="section release-feature">
    <div class="release-art reveal">
      <img src="/assets/a-little-light-a-little-grace.jpg" alt="A Little Light, A Little Grace cover artwork" />
    </div>
    <div class="release-copy reveal delay-1">
      <p class="eyebrow">Featured song</p>
      <h2>A Little Light,<br />A Little Grace</h2>
      <p class="lead">A quiet acceptance that love does not have to occupy the whole world to be real, generous, or lasting.</p>
      <p>Intimate acoustic storytelling shaped by restraint, warmth, and the difficult grace of letting another person remain fully themselves.</p>
      <a class="text-link" href="https://distrokid.com/hyperfollow/paganinorth/a-little-light-a-little-grace" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Listen everywhere <span>↗</span></a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="ghost" class="section album-feature">
    <div class="album-copy reveal">
      <p class="eyebrow">Album and title track</p>
      <h2>The Ghost<br />of the Boy</h2>
      <p class="album-line">Some lives are not lost. They are buried so another life can continue.</p>
      <div class="story-columns">
        <p>Sometimes we have to put away the life that might have been in order to be present for the life that depends on us. There is a price for that.</p>
        <p>The title track lives in the moment when someone comes along and brings that forgotten part of you back into the light.</p>
      </div>
      <a class="button button-outline" href="https://distrokid.com/hyperfollow/paganinorth/the-ghost-of-the-boy" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Listen to the album</a>
    </div>
    <div class="album-promo reveal delay-1">
      <img src="/assets/the-ghost-of-the-boy-promo.jpg" alt="The Ghost of the Boy by Pagani North, available now" />
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section behind-song">
    <div class="behind-copy reveal">
      <p class="eyebrow">Behind the song</p>
      <h2>A song written from the place where memory and responsibility collide.</h2>
      <p class="lead">The title track is about the cost of becoming who life required you to be, and what happens when someone awakens the person you once had to forget.</p>
      <p>The chords are shared for anyone who wants to play the song.</p>
      <div class="actions">
        <a class="button button-primary" href="/assets/the-ghost-of-the-boy-handwritten-chords.pdf" target="_blank">View the chords</a>
        <a class="button button-ghost" href="/story#behind-the-song">Read the full story</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <a class="artifact-preview reveal delay-1" href="/assets/the-ghost-of-the-boy-handwritten-chords.pdf" target="_blank" aria-label="Open chord chart PDF">
      <img src="/assets/the-ghost-of-the-boy-handwritten-preview.jpg" alt="First page of the chord chart for The Ghost of the Boy" />
      <span>Chord chart · 4 pages</span>
    </a>
  </section>

  <section class="section quote-section">
    <blockquote class="reveal">“The past cost too much to remember.”</blockquote>
    <p class="quote-note reveal delay-1">From <em>The Ghost of the Boy</em></p>
  </section>

  <section class="section closing-cta">
    <div class="reveal">
      <p class="eyebrow">Pagani North</p>
      <h2>Stay close to the songs.</h2>
      <p>New releases, stories behind the music, and occasional notes from quiet rooms.</p>
      <a class="button button-primary" href="mailto:hello@paganinorth.com">hello@paganinorth.com</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
